      <title>高盛策略师表示增长是欧洲股市的主要风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/goldman-strategists-say-growth-is-key-risk-for-european-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团策略师表示，欧洲股市面临经济放缓导致的回调风险，这种回调将抵消降息带来的提振作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/goldman-strategists-say-growth-is-key-risk-for-european-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 08:28:05 GMT</pubDate>
